{
  "stem": "1753.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 134.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Finally, I took the whole thing, including the gun.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Put everything in that knapsack.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We left, go deeper into the forest.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Now, I dropped the carbine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I said, I don't need it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Now as I said to myself, in case there's an encounter-- If I have a carbine, my chances is somebody would be scared.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It's that-- you don't calculate that careful, but you make quick judgement and you react to it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It was also too heavy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And in those days, I didn't know that well how to run-- use one either.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Afterwards I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And the front comes closer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Then I walk, I see some bodies laying there, right there in between, you know, the-- the forest and there's a road right between another road.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "A man was laying there with his hair falling off from the heat and all this, and I saw another one.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But you're so hardened, you don't-- it doesn't affect you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "You know, like for example, I was in that barrack A, I told you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And we were lined up there, 25 on every layer, where under normal circumstances maybe only six could lay comfortably.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We wake up in the morning, you know, and the guy next door to you is dead.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "You don't worry about him, just look what kind of shoes they have.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "They're better than you, or his jacket better than yours or whatever you have.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "You can't get emotional in things like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I guess that's built in-- in to you-- to you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "You got to be strong, otherwise you only worry about yourself then, basically.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "You worry about collectively but when it comes really down to-- to [INAUDIBLE], it's survival.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
